Since $\angle BDC = 3x,$ $\angle BDA = \angle CDA = 180^\circ - 3x.$

Since $\angle BDA + \angle B = 180^\circ,$ $\angle ADB = 90^\circ - \frac{x}{2} = \angle B.$

